faa9873c","tid":488170,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T05:54:41.000Z","msg":"我最憎枝吉他無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3117b86c64933473d9d4fe8c4e50659f9af048","tid":488170,"uid":106510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:02:49.000Z","msg":"唔同層面無得比較<br />\n<br />\n檸檬係keep住柒但佢唔認為自己柒<br />\n<br />\n關家姐都知衰 但單次柒既程度係前無古人後無來者"},{"pid":"462c401744f75ee45cef532b6b660c6d962e3023","tid":488170,"uid":55519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"檸檬真係走火入魔 十幾歲中二病都算 到到兒家都唔細 仲有小朋友 都仲可以咁自我中心 <br />\n所以人地話當有傻人做傻事搏人注意 我地唔應該拍手、歡呼 應該視若無睹 咁佢先會自我檢討"},{"pid":"a143b739177a474f9be49f38ba4a0823a32b03b7","tid":488170,"uid":27451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點會柒得過關家姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起碼檸檬的片你可以睇完再睇，一笑再笑<br />\n<br />\n家姐條片我第一次睇個時，覺得佢好柒但係一的都笑唔出重好sad，之後一直無勇氣睇第二次<br />\n<br />\n依家諗起個畫面都重會起雞皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bec2ed40759358e26b729976fdb95f3cee14c9","tid":488170,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔同<br />\n睇關家姐柒會尷尬,可憐佢<br />\n檸檬柒係真心想笑鳩佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關家姐都係柒一次姐，但檸檬條柒頭就出親㴝都要柒下咁。"},{"pid":"060700270d2012c751ab655e348d9759bc239328","tid":488170,"uid":27451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/132737_3f8f490d4ebdf57a3ac63974ee785e56.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F132737_3f8f490d4ebdf57a3ac63974ee785e56.gi