:15:44.000Z","msg":"人哋英文好到去大學講talk"},{"pid":"68acc3cdd682fe5ab6e88a532e4743c16f976123","tid":488170,"uid":31530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"我都想好似佢咁柒<br />\n但有咁既成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔介意"},{"pid":"58fb647fbbc6af45cd8450fab143c63f19260a96","tid":488170,"uid":27451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人哋英文好到去大學講talk</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nso?<br />\n咁就可以唔柒？"},{"pid":"109704668e20a8fa691c22824203e469ee1c1d66","tid":488170,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想好似佢咁柒<br />\n但有咁既成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔介意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n檸檬咁撚鐘意奶蝗，但連乜鳩係知恥近乎勇都唔識，奶乜鳩蝗呀？"},{"pid":"b6af17316d65fe8d2cf15afaaf4feb14c9062559","tid":488170,"uid":43936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:33:33.000Z","msg":"但係佢柒得黎我會想睇多幾次<br />\n相反關家姐段片除左直播個次，一次都唔敢睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af46d0f96b1e2d1436f0db17131c265f254b17ae","tid":488170,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係佢柒得黎我會想睇多幾次<br />\n相反關家姐段片除左直播個次，一次都唔敢睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好咁啦，關家姐都好慘架。"},{"pid":"acb00efb2bd7e0d585d7bb77c1b7862280befd80","tid":488170,"uid":1130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MaBQze9rdrw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaBQze9rdrw&d=rKcJJVa6SMWng0bfshvUrgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=756386a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MaBQze9rdrw</a>"},{"pid":"4e53076c84cd22e5629805d7558782e4f4cab3d6","tid":488170,"uid":61030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"霆鋒嗰隻柒係有意識，故意去做<br />\n而關家姐嗰隻無心柒係最柒嘅境界"},{"pid":"0d46c737f4c667666f76e09a662df935c9ac6c78","tid":488170,"uid":152156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/MaBQze9rdrw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaBQze9rdrw&d=rKcJJVa6SMWng0bfshvUrgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=756386a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MaBQze9rdrw</a></blockquote><br />\n其實最後個下先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5d6fe038ba21c2bd0b3b461369d8c653cfac33","tid":488170,"uid":7638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最憎枝吉他無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記得好似話枝野仲要係貴野黎"},{"pid":"cbd8871114036ed4f5378485338ebf2c6f49998a","tid":488170,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我最憎枝吉他無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記得好似話枝野仲要係貴野黎</blockquote><br />\n果時已經大把錢 幾架法拉利 頂包完先無揸車 一枝吉他幾十萬算乜錢 夠型少少錢扺掟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b4fdd05752f77d20f896a5005409ca45ef718b","tid":488170,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:20:30.000Z","msg":"好地地有歌唔唱有戲唔拍做乜尻廚神<br />\n痴撚線又唔係有米芝連扮乜撚？"},{"pid":"1ca803a5f02aa74ca9a49946fb1f239e5efd4329","tid":488170,"uid":71703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點會柒得過關家姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起碼檸檬的片你可以睇完再睇，一笑再笑<br />\n<br />\n家姐條片我第一次睇個時，覺得佢好柒但係一的都笑唔出重好sad，之後一直無勇氣睇第二次<br />\n<br />\n依家諗起個畫面都重會起雞皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩 真係完全形容到果個境界<br />\n檸檬真係去唔到果個柒既 level<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32df4707d63b40732cdc8ae6eb896ad469686d1","tid":488170,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:28:27.000Z","msg":"早幾年拍戲我覺得佢好大進步<br />\n成熟好多<br />\n但而家係回到話去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd819cb19f827c4b1ab37d9f6c266e911843974c","tid":488170,"uid":34069,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:33:21.000Z","msg":"人地真係柒得起，拍戲音樂生意英文樣樣得<br />\n你地鐘意笑咪慢慢笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見過佢真人，超毒撚look但好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831c4d92d1ee794e1f00c8f92a7e077146647d4a","tid":488170,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好地地有歌唔唱有戲唔拍做乜尻廚神<br />\n痴撚線又唔係有米芝連扮乜撚？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝗鍾意睇呢d傻鳩扮野架。"},{"pid":"4aa6e8c7c647667bdd712a4833171f46ce4ccbab","tid":488170,"uid":121240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"原本都覺得家姐好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但之後工作關係經常見到佢 好好禮貌冇架子 就完全唔想再笑佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c596d73a8457ea2f6735a45c75281e97c88d823","tid":488170,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關家姐真係冇勇氣睇多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d26d97116c7ffb0c2bd23599d3f92de6195282c","tid":488170,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:41:22.